dfischer.utils

Class LoadtestPluginStaticHashtable

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.LoadtestPluginStaticHashtable

  • public class LoadtestPluginStaticHashtable
extends java.lang.Object
    A static hashtable that can be used by load test plug-ins. The key is implemented as a String, the data type of the value is Object.
     
    Note about synchronisation: This class synchronizes keys and references to objects only, but not any data fields inside objects. If you get a reference to an object - for example by calling get(key) - and then update any data field of that object, such an update is NOT synchronized because ist happens "outside" of this class.
    See Also:
    Hashtable
